CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, on December 27, 1969, reads: "DANDY DUFFERS PARTY - Gathered at the Club Loendi, in a recent social hour, were these members of the Dandy Duffers Golf and Country Club...."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of members of the Dandy Duffers Golf club holding trophies and gathered in Loendi Club, including unknown man, Kathleen Holloway, Aurelia Johnson, and another man, possibly Charles Hinton
